Program: Start the Week
Title: 06/10/2008
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00dqlhg
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 6 Oct 2008
Andrew Marr sets the cultural agenda for the week. Featuring Chris Patten talking about his new book What Next? How to Survive the 21st Century, the writer Xinran discusses the growing generation gap in China, and the historian Andrew Roberts and biographer Richard Holmes talk about their new books. Show less